{"tid":169310,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂討論區#20:衛藤美彩写真集発売決定","createTime":"2017-03-24T06:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T06:25:58.000Z","uid":8431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df4e221a6e20e19b5676e9786d660b216104aab0","tid":169310,"uid":8431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:24:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">LIHK乃PO呼籲:<br />\n 「Misa寫真集4月25發售」</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8o61qjS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8o61qjS.jpg&h=fd2df7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3oLzwS5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3oLzwS5.jpg&h=10099491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一期生、二期與三期生在內，團體目前共有47名成員，而隊長為櫻井玲香。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團體名稱中的「乃木坂」是唱片公司日本索尼音樂（SME）總部大樓的所在地。<br />\n根據秋元康所說，<span style=\"color: red;\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。 <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成員名單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nogizaka46.com%2Fmember%2F&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=54b9a038\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M192y0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM192y0.gif&h=91a8a043&s={SIZE}\" /></div></span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/QLOU8B7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQLOU8B7.png&h=3cdca041&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">乃木坂46 17thシングル「インフルエンサー」<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42N6f0Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42N6f0Z.jpg&h=af429949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白石麻衣2nd寫真集 「パスポート」 <span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/nogizaka46bunno1/imgs/5/3/5366676f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fnogizaka46bunno1%2Fimgs%2F5%2F3%2F5366676f.jpg&h=413b775a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n橋本奈々未2nd寫真集 「2017」<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fa6VczV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffa6VczV.jpg&h=93550f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秋元真夏 寫真集 「真夏の気圧配置」<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ntfXtlB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FntfXtlB.jpg&h=8570ebda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n桜井玲香 寫真集 「自由ということ」<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46成員列表17TH VER.(最新)</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gZ9zdMV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgZ9zdMV.png&h=c5e98073&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46三期生</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/le1YeCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fle1YeCG.jpg&h=50053a09&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnogizaka46-dc.com%2Fsort%2F&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=92ae8234\" target=\"_blank\">http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n <br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購,，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n <br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員,但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n <br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本參加握手會、演唱會，不要幻想他們來港舉辦握手會，因為此舉極為傻豬。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n <br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦?<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/24/142215_3dc82133c0720c10eca2e65054bc11e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F24%2F142215_3dc82133c0720c10eca2e65054bc11e4.jpg&h=433e65b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/24/142327_74eb98d77be40070ca6430cb3812db24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F24%2F142327_74eb98d77be40070ca6430cb3812db24.jpg&h=fa5ef5e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TEMPLATE:</span></span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3456e44a\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"479b228e9517feb3aeec9b75d72fdb59318f4363","tid":169310,"uid":8431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:25:11.000Z","msg":"TITLE柒左重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc80e4ae011d7311fccdd201875725d58684f732","tid":169310,"uid":1986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"Black number<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}